short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export your Linkedin Leads information in a click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension provides a sales feature to save Linkedin leads contact details to Unlead.ai dashboard CRM directly without leaving Linkedin. It also supports exporting leads in bulk from LinkedIn Sales navigator to Unlead.ai dashboard CRM.
It is also an additional useful feature for the Unlead.ai Dashboard users to access and get notified whenever their sales prospects open and interact with emails they have been sent via Unlead.ai platform. The extension user just have to login with their Unlead.ai credentials on the extension and they will see the activities that happened for last 30 days.
